OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter officer struck by stolen police
OL,5,Ccar
OL,7,FA man has been charged with attempted
OL,8,Fmurder after an officer was struck by
OL,9,Fa stolen police car.
OL,11,FThe officer sustained what police
OL,12,Fdescribed as serious injuries in the
OL,13,Fcollision in Downpatrick at the
OL,14,Fweekend.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
