CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780517152
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter officer struck by stolen police
OL,5,Ccar
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, police said a 36-year-
OL,8,Fold man had been charged with
OL,9,Fattempted murder, aggravated vehicle
OL,10,Ftaking causing injury, aggravated
OL,11,Fvehicle taking in which vehicle is
OL,12,Fdriven dangerously and a number of
OL,13,Fadditional driving offences.
OL,15,FHe is due to appear at Downpatrick
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday.
OL,18,FA police spokesperson said: "As is
OL,19,Fusual procedure, the charges will be
OL,20,Freviewed by the Public Prosecution
OL,21,FService."
OL,26,@zD@]OU}D@IO]
