OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter officer struck by stolen police
OL,5,Ccar
OL,7,FMeanwhile, on Monday, Kieran Turley,
OL,8,F27, from Vianstown Road in
OL,9,FDownpatrick, appeared before the
OL,10,Ftown's magistrates' court charged with
OL,11,Fdangerous driving, driving while
OL,12,Fdisqualified and using a motor vehicle
OL,13,Fwith no insurance.
OL,15,FHe was remanded in custody to appear
OL,16,Fin court again later in June.
